snippet.title: Dagada's Story Trailer V2
snippet.description:
New version of the trailer of the indie game: Dagada's Story.

A great adventure in the Super Nintendo era awaits you! Dagada will explore a treacherous mountain and solve the mysterious puzzles of ancient ruins to find his way home. But the threat of a dangerous climate looms! Will you help him restore harmony to this once peaceful nature turned hostile?

You can follow the progress of the game dev here:
* x.com/Maluska19
* store.steampowered.com/app/1859390/Dagadas_Story/
